> It is a violation of the IDE and ATAPI specs to have a device alone on a
> channel set to slave operation, although most CD-ROM devices will work this
> way.  Set the CD-ROM to be a master device instead of a slave and see if
> the behaviour changes.  I have seen this problem before in this situation.
